03/01/84  display_component_name, dcn

Syntax:  dcn path offsets


Function: converts an offset within a bound segment into offset within
the referenced component object.


Arguments:
path
   is the pathname of a bound object segment or an octal segment
   number.  A pathname that looks like an octal segment can be
   specified by -name nnn.
offsets
   are octal offsets within the text of the bound object segment
   specified by the path argument.
